+# Phase 2.18 — Route Incident Bundle → Vertex RCA Bridge
+
+## Цель
+Преобразовать forensic bundle по route-governance incident в compact Vertex RCA input и получить structured RCA result.
+
+## Компоненты
+- `operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_to_vertex_bridge_v2_18.py`
+- `vertex_routing_incident_route_rca_provider_v2_18.py`
+- `ml_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_orchestrator_v2_18.py`
+
+## Потоки
+- input: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle_results`
+- request: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_requests`
+- result: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_results`
+- proposals: `stream:ml:recommendation_proposals`
+- dlq: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_dlq`
+
+## Safe start
+```bash
+export VERTEX_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_DRY_RUN=1
+export VERTEX_PROJECT_ID=...
+export VERTEX_LOCATION=global
+export VERTEX_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash-lite
+```
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle_results + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_requests + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_results + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:recommendation_proposals + - COUNT 3
+curl -s localhost:9900/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_bridge_'
+curl -s localhost:9901/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_'
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- advisory-only
+- proposals выходят review-only
